question:
Let the initial value of count be 5. What will be the final value of count if the instructions are executed in the following order: S1;T1;S2;T2;S3;T3? 
 Process P0:
{
S1: register1=count;
S2: register1=register1 - 5
S3: count=register1
}
Process P1:
{
T1: register2=count;
T2: register2=register2 X 5
T3: count=register2
}
